item.title:
Instagram is working on a Twitter competitor that will be released this summer, Bloomberg reports.
The text-based app is currently being tested with creators and celebrities.

item.title: One year ago today, Harry Styles released his third studio album ‘Harry’s House.’
item.author: PopBase

item.title: The Grammy-nominated album spawned hits like ‘Dangerous Woman,’ ‘Into You’ and ‘Side To Side.’ It has amassed over 5 billion streams on Spotify and is certified 2x Platinum in the US.
